condition.narrative: The Recipient shall, not later 3 months from the Effectiveness Date establish and thereafter maintain throughout the implementationof the Project, a Project Steering Committee (PSC) with a composition, mandate, terms of reference and resources satisfactory tothe Association. Without limitation to the foregoing, the PSC shall meet four times per year and shall be co-chaired by the ChiefMinisters of the Ministry of Finance and the Ministry of Communications, or their designees, and shall include the Chief Directorsof key participating Ministries and selected private sector representatives. The PSC will be supported by the projectimplementation unit of the Ministry of Communications on operational matters and by a Technical Committee.
